<TABLE BORDER=0 cellpadding=4 border=0 cellspacing=0 WIDTH="95%"><TR ><TD COLSPAN=2><CENTER><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="#F0DCA0" FACE="Verdana, Arial">T O P I C  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; R E V I E W</font></CENTER></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtextureL.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">silverkitfox</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">1st of all, kudos to Larian Studios for one helluva RPG.  Anyway, let me get down to business.  As I was exploring the area around Captain Mitox, I ventured towards the west.  There was this nearby camp or armory depot, so I decided to go in.  Immediately after entry, an old dude suddenly appears from nowhere, smack in the middle of the camp, then blurts out.."ah the Marked One.  Let's see if you can handle this ish..." or sumthin like that (I forgot the exact words).  Then, two accomplices, a female and a male(?) thing(elf, dwarf, though definitely not a human/orc/lizard) appear behind him.  They mumble some mumbo-jumbo then they mind-control ALL (as in ALL) the soldiers in that area..and turned them against me!!! All the soldiers now appear red in my mini-map and are hostile.  Right before they start attacking...someone mumbles "Kill the civilian..." which most probably was me.  Anyway, I haven't talked to Mitox before this event, I just went straight to the west camp...then this event I just described just happened.  What do I do?  Do I kill all these soldiers?  Do I leave them alone, fulfill a quest that might appease them?  Or find where the three magicians (the old dude, the chick and the chicken) and confront them (they immediately teleported somewhere right after mind-controlling the soldiers)?  Please hit me up ASAP.  I need your help!!!  THANKS!!!!</FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtexture.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">DireWolf</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">You can kill all the soldiers, or just l